## Acceptance criteria

* All Sales Agent return paths validate against `SalesAnalysisResult` before output.
* Invalid LLM JSON and invalid recommendations are never returned as-is.
* Empty-sales fallback from Step 7.2 passes the same validation gate.
* Mock and real LLM paths share the same validation logic.
* No validation bypass in tests or development mode.
* Focused unit tests cover the cases listed above.
* `docs/phases/step-7.3.md` exists.
* Step 7.4 example output doc is not implemented in this step.
